    <item>
      <title>摩根大通对过渡融资给出“不”的微妙回答</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-02/jpmorgan-offers-a-nuanced-no-on-transition-financing-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社的阿拉斯泰尔·马什 (Alastair Marsh) 报道称，摩根大通 (JPMorgan Chase &amp; Co.) 并不拒绝为碳基能源的替代品提供融资的想法。但马什在“彭博未平仓合约”上表示，该银行专注于支持赢家，并且没有遵循同行为指导投资而制定的框架。索纳利·巴萨克 (Sonali Basak) 的“华尔街快讯”通讯于周五发布。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-02/jpmorgan-offers-a-nuanced-no-on-transition-financing-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 15:46:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃莱克特拉股价暴跌 60%，萨利纳斯市一天内将损失 40 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/salinas-set-to-lose-4-billion-in-a-day-as-elektra-slumps-60</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在监管机构下令交易所在长期暂停交易后恢复交易后，Grupo Elektra 股价周一暴跌逾 60%，亿万富翁里卡多·萨利纳斯·普利戈 (Ricardo Salinas Pliego) 的财富因此蒸发约 40 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/salinas-set-to-lose-4-billion-in-a-day-as-elektra-slumps-60</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 15:43:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Castle Water 将提供 40 亿英镑股权以拯救泰晤士水务公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/castle-water-to-offer-4-billion-equity-to-rescue-thames-water</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Castle Water Ltd. 本周将向泰晤士水务公司注资 40 亿英镑（51 亿美元），以帮助这家陷入困境的公用事业公司免于破产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/castle-water-to-offer-4-billion-equity-to-rescue-thames-water</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 13:01:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>挪威碳捕获工厂实现长船项目里程碑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/norway-carbon-capture-plant-marks-milestone-in-longship-project</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威政府表示，海德堡材料股份公司位于挪威布雷维克水泥厂的碳捕获工厂已完全组装完毕，这标志着 26 亿美元北海碳排放封存计划取得了重要里程碑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/norway-carbon-capture-plant-marks-milestone-in-longship-project</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 11:29:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
